{"word":"ὑποποιέω","slug":"ὑποποιέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποποιέω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to put under</i>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to subject to oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to produce gradually</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to gain by underhand tricks, to win over</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to assume, affect</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}